{"tid":586914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「那話兒比我老公小」　志工媽媽外遇替代役男","createTime":"2018-03-10T03:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T04:30:37.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"497e5aadd831f83da332cddfdcc7bbdb2a968a2f","tid":586914,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"《自由時報》報導，桃園市蘇姓替代役男，5年多前服役時認識大他21歲的志工媽媽，2人相戀並發生性行為，因頻繁通聯被女方丈夫抓包。<br />\n<br />\n儘管蘇男否認當小王卻遭婦人打臉，出庭指證他「下面比較細小，比我老公的小」、「帶我上摩鐵，想陪我度過世界末日」。<br />\n<br />\n桃園地院去年5月依妨害家庭罪判蘇男4月徒刑，婦人因丈夫撤告獲不起訴處分；法官昨就民事部分，以蘇男侵害婦人丈夫婚姻權，判決應賠償15萬元。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.amazonaws.com/br-cdn/temp_images/2013/12/04/suarez3rd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.amazonaws.com%2Fbr-cdn%2Ftemp_images%2F2013%2F12%2F04%2Fsuarez3rd.gif&h=d1b77e83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cc105d2f9018d66237cb48da0638dd1d3f3f862","tid":586914,"uid":19360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所</span></span>"},{"pid":"4a83f5f1eabd27f57b0a0045c98deab8c7e1fc30","tid":586914,"uid":38352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cc105d2f9018d66237cb48da0638dd1d3f3f862","tid":586914,"uid":19360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以</span></span>"},{"pid":"40600f9b795d3038342299514dcfccedce997434","tid":586914,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a83f5f1eabd27f57b0a0045c98deab8c7e1fc30","tid":586914,"uid":38352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cc105d2f9018d66237cb48da0638dd1d3f3f862","tid":586914,"uid":19360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"<s